text: While Kelly won't be on the air until June, she's already started working at NBC. She tweeted a photo of herself outside the company's headquarters last month, writing "First day on the job @NBCNews! On the air in June, but had so much fun meeting new colleagues today. Grateful. Happy."
title: Burying The Hatchet! Megyn Kelly Welcomed With Open Arms By Hoda Kotb And The 'TODAY' Show
